{
  "stem": "21437.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If it was the washing, if it was the carrying-- whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was not really--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were working on the road--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For the men was on the road and unprotected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, because of the weather-- you know, sometimes, after all, they were hungry all the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we had some Dutch people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The last part was-- the last couple of months, we had some Dutch, Dutch inmates-- Dutch prisoners coming.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now I remember this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, in the beginning, they could not touch-- they said, this is food?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We don't-- we'd rather starve.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't want to touch it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we were already-- our bodies were already apparently partly used to it, or really craved-- any little bit that-- even a drink.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a time when a drink of water-- you went to have a bit of water, you felt full.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't want to touch it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But a few days later, there were some rubbish bins, you know, where-- they were going through the rubbish bins and looking for-- and they didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They did not survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They could not survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They could not survive this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they died, died of infections-- starve-- they couldn't-- the food that was there, it only very little offered.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was barely to keep you alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, you see, for them it was not enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or they did not--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went gradually, you see?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were sort of, you know-- gradually, this was less, this was less.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or even-- if what happened in the beginning, somehow the family provided certain things where it made it easier for you to accept it.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
